    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>RenderMan requires certain AOVs to be enabled for the denoiser to work correctly on batch renders.  </p><p>These AOVs can be applied in 2 ways.</p><p>Either with a <em>rendermanrendervars </em>node or via the <em>rendermanrendersettings </em>node.  Both are valid workflows.</p><p>The Denoiser AOVs needs to be activated, and the easiest way to do this is by clicking the blue R in the top right corner (highlighted red in the images below)</p><p>This will enable all AOVs required by the Denoiser.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_SolarisRenderVars.jpg\" width=\"1800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_SolarisRenderVars.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761648501173&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=760\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641829/RenderMan_SolarisRenderVars.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761648501173&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"790\" data-width=\"1871\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"634290375\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_SolarisRenderVars.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641829\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"8\" data-media-id=\"4c128710-acc6-4fcf-8c28-ea3953c45501\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_SolarisRenderVars.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761648501173&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1871&amp;height=790 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_SolarisRenderVars.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761648501173&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=760 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_denoiser_Setup2.jpg\" width=\"1800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_denoiser_Setup2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761649171136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=847\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_denoiser_Setup2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761649171136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"875\" data-width=\"1859\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"634290387\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_denoiser_Setup2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641829\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"8\" data-media-id=\"d7078a0c-5840-4bf5-b8ff-0649bac63625\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_denoiser_Setup2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761649171136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1859&amp;height=875 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_denoiser_Setup2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761649171136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=847 1x\"></span><p /><p>Once you have activated the required denoising AOVS, you can do one of the following two setups:</p><hr/><p>Setup 1 - ROP Fetch Node</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_1.jpg\" width=\"1341\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1341&amp;height=670\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"745\" data-width=\"1491\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544641850\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641829\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"8\" data-media-id=\"bd7d575a-ea9d-483c-b52f-8db21f981742\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1491&amp;height=745 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1341&amp;height=670 1x\"></span><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>In the OUT context, create a ROP <em>fetch</em> node</p></li><li><p>Set the <em>Source</em> parameter to a desired desired LOP <em>usdrender_rop</em> node in the Solaris/Stage context.</p></li><li><p>Connect a ROP <em>denoise</em> node to the ROP <em>fetch</em> node input.</p></li><li><p>On the ROP <em>denoise</em> node, set mode type, output location, asymmetry, flow and debug options, and once ready to render, press the Denoise button.<br/><br/>Houdini will render the LOP <em>usdrender_rop</em> node using the frame range on the <em>denoise</em> node. Once all the frames have been rendered, the denoise process will begin.</p></li></ol><p /><hr/><p>Setup 2 - ROP USD Render Node</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_2.jpg\" width=\"1341\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1341&amp;height=1157\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1290\" data-width=\"1494\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544641847\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641829\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"8\" data-media-id=\"4beabe31-f2ba-4c70-b4a5-3861eb75f2ec\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1494&amp;height=1290 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Solaris_Denoise_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1341&amp;height=1157 1x\"></span><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>In the OUT context, create a ROP <em>usdrender</em> node, and change the render delegate to RenderMan RIS (XPU rendering is not currently supported with denoising in Solaris)</p></li><li><p>Set the<em> LOP path </em>parameter to a desired node in the Solaris/Stage context where some <em>RenderSettings</em> primitive exist (the most probable default case will be <em>/stage/rendermanrendersettings</em>)</p></li><li><p>Set the <em>Render Settings</em> parameter to the location in your scene graph tree where the desired <em>RenderSettings</em> primitive is (the most probable default case will be /Render/rendersettings)</p></li><li><p>Connect a ROP <em>denoise</em> node to the ROP usdrender node input</p></li><li><p>On the ROP <em>denoise</em> node, set your desired parameters, and click the denoise button to begin rendering the frames to disc and denoise.</p></li></ol><p style=\"margin-left: 30.0px;\">Houdini will render the ROP <em>usdrender</em> node using the frame range on the <em>denoise</em> node. Once all the frames have been rendered, the denoise process will begin.</p><p /><hr/><p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"73f72c7c-16d5-4d65-9d8b-bcbb0bf1d622\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Note : At this time we do not support the denoising workflow for Solaris in TOPs / PDG yet</p></div></div><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_noised.jpg\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_noised.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641829/RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_noised.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544641844\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_noised.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641829\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"8\" data-media-id=\"dbe58c0d-e329-4cd5-bf71-7880da42e737\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_noised.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1372&amp;height=770 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_noised.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_denoised.jpg\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_denoised.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641829/RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_denoised.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544641841\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_denoised.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641829\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"8\" data-media-id=\"8ef87b4c-5f1c-4984-9a2b-e22cc4e94a3c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_denoised.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1372&amp;height=770 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641829/RenderMan_Studio_rough_Close_denoised.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433094080&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/>1920 x 1080<br/>Pixel Variance = 0.26<br/>Max Samples = 64</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
